      "latex": "\\mathbf{H}_{\\mathbf{X}}[f]=\\nabla_{\\mathbf{X}}\\left[\\left(\\nabla_{\\mathbf{X}}[f]\\right)^{T}\\right]=\\frac{\\partial^{2}f}{\\partial\\mathbf{x}\\partial\\mathbf{x}^{T}}=\\left(\\begin{array}{c c c}\\frac{\\partial^{2}f}{\\partial x_{1}^{2}}&\\cdots&\\frac{\\partial^{2}f}{\\partial x_{1}\\partial x_{n}}\\\\ \\vdots&\\ddots&\\vdots\\\\ \\frac{\\partial^{2}f}{\\partial x_{1}\\partial x_{n}}&\\cdots&\\frac{\\partial^{2}f}{\\partial x_{n}^{2}}\\end{array}\\right)",
